OL,3,CCouncil tax rise and new flood fund
OL,4,Cproposed by Leicestershire County
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FLeicestershire County Council has
OL,8,Fpublished fresh budget proposals,
OL,9,Foutlining a multi-million pound
OL,10,Finvestment in services while
OL,11,Fconfirming a 4.99% rise in Council Tax
OL,12,Ffrom April.
OL,14,FThe Conservative-run council says the
OL,15,Fplan is designed to support vulnerable
OL,16,Fpeople, fix potholes, and tackle
OL,17,Fflooding, but financial challenges
OL,18,Floom on the horizon.
