OL,7,FRoad maintenance will also see a
OL,8,Fboost, with an additional #12 million
OL,9,Fset aside to repair potholes and
OL,10,Fimprove infrastructure.
OL,12,FFollowing the severe New Year floods,
OL,13,Fthe council is proposing a #1 million
OL,14,Finvestment to help communities clean
OL,15,Fup and better prepare for future
OL,16,Fflooding.
