OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FThis would fund investigations into
OL,8,Fflood causes, drainage repairs, and
OL,9,Fdebris clearance, with a further half-
OL,10,Fa-million pounds allocated for
OL,11,Fimmediate drainage works by April.
OL,13,FTo balance the books next year,
OL,14,Freserves will be used to plug a small
OL,15,Fbudget gap. However, the council warns
OL,16,Fthat by 2027, this gap could widen to
OL,17,F#38 million and reach #91 million by
OL,18,F2029.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
