OL,7,FShe said: "Our focus has to be
OL,8,Fmanaging what's in our gift and
OL,9,Fremaining financially resilient.
OL,11,F"We're investing big sums of money in
OL,12,Fsupporting vulnerable people,
OL,13,Fdirecting as much as we can into
OL,14,Fservices we know our residents value,
OL,15,Fsuch as mending potholes and
OL,16,Fsupporting flood-hit communities."
