OL,7,FCllr Taylor also called on the
OL,8,FGovernment to take stronger action on
OL,9,Fflooding: "Flooding is heartbreaking
OL,10,Ffor our residents and businesses, with
OL,11,Fmany counting the costs for the second
OL,12,For third time in just a year. So it's
OL,13,Fonly right that we help them to
OL,14,Frecover and invest in bolstering
OL,15,Fcommunities' resilience.
OL,17,F"But we need Government to grip the
OL,18,Fissue. We've written to the flooding
OL,19,Fminister calling to overhaul the
OL,20,Fnational approach and we need action."
