OL,7,FCouncillor Lee Breckon, cabinet member
OL,8,Ffor resources, highlighted the
OL,9,Frelentless strain on council finances
OL,10,Fsaying: "The pressure on councils'
OL,11,Fbudgets is relentless. The National
OL,12,FLiving Wage and National Insurance
OL,13,Fchanges alone add around #20 million
OL,14,Fto our costs next year.
OL,16,F"This includes what we need to pay our
OL,17,Fcare providers, which is not funded by
OL,18,FGovernment."
