OL,7,FBUDGET BREAKDOWN
OL,9,FWhile the council is taking steps to
OL,10,Fbalance its budget for the coming
OL,11,Fyear, financial challenges remain.
OL,13,FWith growing service demands and
OL,14,Funcertainty over future funding,
OL,15,Fresidents will likely feel the impact
OL,16,Fof both the investments and the cost-
OL,17,Fsaving measures in the years ahead.
