OL,7,FThe government has said: "We are
OL,8,Finjecting #69 billion of funding into
OL,9,Fcouncil budgets across England to help
OL,10,Fthem drive forward the government's
OL,11,FPlan for Change, including a #34.5
OL,12,Fmillion increase for Leicestershire
OL,13,FCounty Council.
OL,15,F"We know that councils have suffered
OL,16,Ffrom short-term solutions, which is
OL,17,Fwhy we are working hand in hand with
OL,18,Fcouncils to reform this outdated
OL,19,Fsystem and fix teh foundations of
OL,20,Flocal governmentment."
